{"tid":1191584,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"內陸機機票同回鄉證唔同名，點算？","createTime":"2019-06-08T04:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T04:52:54.000Z","uid":188194,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91973f52b6c67a964d7e92ea4ee8c9f872b3fe12","tid":1191584,"uid":188194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"我前排經traveliker訂咗飛香港上海來回機票（中國東方航空公司）。但訂嗰時用咗ID同passport嘅英文名(e.g. Chan, David Tai Man)，但個名同回鄉證上嘅英文名唔同(e.g. Chan, Tai Man)。想請問下check in攞機票嘅話，係咪主要睇回鄉證？係嘅話，咁我係咪將機票名改用回鄉證個名就ok?"},{"pid":"3b482351ebaff59dbfaea820d112e967a583d66e","tid":1191584,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"比利時"},{"pid":"04c14cf66516114ea8f097270acb98579c39e57f","tid":1191584,"uid":241293,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"首先其實香港飛大陸唔算內陸機<br />\n不過Check in 只會同你檢查回鄉證<br />\n所以要同回鄉證同名<br />\n<br />\n不過你身分證同回鄉證唔同名其實好麻煩，最好就快啲改返啦"},{"pid":"15e39dd7897891ae514abc01fc93bab04f2f05c5","tid":1191584,"uid":188194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c14cf66516114ea8f097270acb98579c39e57f","tid":1191584,"uid":241293,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"首先其實香港飛大陸唔算內陸機<br />\n不過Check in 只會同你檢查回鄉證<br />\n所以要同回鄉證同名<br />\n<br />\n不過你身分證同回鄉證唔同名其實好麻煩，最好就快啲改返啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"感謝你嘅reply !!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f9b4c06837d641ac6b06bc0f2b760d526972b8","tid":1191584,"uid":147629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"香港飛中國係國際線，香港同強國係不同空域"},{"pid":"66ed75a78d516877abf7b450fbe8f3fdf499f9ff","tid":1191584,"uid":150561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{